  "title": "Operations Manager | Retails Property Management | Shopping Complex (Commercial)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a local leading player in Real Estate Industry, well-known for its diverse portfolio of properties and sustainable urban solutions. They are currently looking for Retail Operations Manager to join the Operations Team. They are located at Central - easily accessible.</strong></p><p>Responsibilities for Retail Operations Manager:</p><ul><li>Lead the Commercial Operations team to develop and execute strategies that enhance asset value across the portfolio.</li><li>Ensure smooth operation of essential services, proper maintenance programs, and staff readiness for fire and life safety systems.</li><li>Review and implement annual Asset Plans for all properties.</li><li>Oversee lease administration, tenant handover/takeover, renovation coordination, and tenant relationship management.</li><li>Prepare annual Operating and CapEx budgets, including forecasts, management reports, and competitor analysis.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Min Degree in Property Management or related studies</li><li>At least 6 year of retail operations experience, handling commercial buildings</li><li>Team player and experience in handling tenant related matter</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.<br /></p><p>Email Address: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
